It was originally used when someone was "going face"in hearthstone. Now it is just used to be generally obnoxious, usually accompanying something in all caps. It's most common use is in in the format BLANK or SMORC. Inwhich the chat demands that the streamer do something or they will otherwise riot with the SMOrc emote.
